13:16.012 --> 13:18.275
IF YOU
HAD NOTHING TO HIDE,

13:18.275 --> 13:20.625
WHY DID YOU LIE
TO THE POLICE AND SAY

13:20.625 --> 13:22.976
YOU WEREN'T AT HER APARTMENT
THE NIGHT SHE DIED?

13:22.976 --> 13:25.021
BECAUSE I KNEW
HOW IT WOULD LOOK.

13:25.021 --> 13:27.545
AND LOOKS LIE...

13:27.545 --> 13:29.809
WHICH IS
