13:29.809 --> 13:32.202
HERE WE ARE.

13:40.994 --> 13:42.343
WHAT WAS THE NATURE
OF YOUR

13:42.343 --> 13:44.519
PERSONAL RELATIONSHIP
WITH CINDY?

13:44.519 --> 13:49.219
