I ADMIRED HER.

13:57.401 --> 14:00.404
YOU ADMIRED
YOUR FLIGHT ATTENDANT?

14:00.404 --> 14:02.885
A COLLEGE DROPOUT?
WHY?

14:02.885 --> 14:06.541
YOU DON'T NEED A COLLEGE DEGREE
TO BE SMART.

14:06.541 --> 14:09.239
CINDY WAS SMART.

14:09.239 --> 14:13.548
SHE'D COME THROUGH
TOUGH CHILDHOOD LIKE I DID.

14:13.548 --> 14:16.420
WE BOTH LEARNED VERY YOUNG
HOW TO LOOK AFTER OURSELVES.

14:16.420 --> 14:20.076
AND I ADMIRED
HER RESILIENCE, HER...

14:20.076 --> 14:21.904
CAPACITY FOR JOY.

14:21.904 --> 14:23.906
IT WAS AMAZING.

14:23.906 --> 14:25.777
YOUR HONOR,
PLEASE EXCUSE

14:25.777 --> 14:27.954
THE INTERRUPTION
OF THE EULOGY HERE,

14:27.954 --> 14:29.607
BUT THE DEFENDANT
HAS NOT BEEN CALLED

14:29.607 --> 14:31.087
AS A CHARACTER WITNESS
FOR THE VICTIM.

14:31.087 --> 14:32.393
SUSTAINED.

14:32.393 --> 14:34.743
I'M SORRY --
WHAT EXACTLY WAS THE OBJECTION

14:34.743 --> 14:36.223
