ARTS-AND-MUSIC FESTIVAL?

16:30.380 --> 16:32.034
OBJECTION. RELEVANCE?

16:32.034 --> 16:33.644
YOUR HONOR, IT GOES TO
THE DEFENDANT'S CREDIBILITY

16:33.644 --> 16:35.907
BY SHOWING HIS PROPENSITY
TO LIE TO THE COURT

16:35.907 --> 16:38.910
AND GENERALLY BEHAVE AS THOUGH
