APPEARANCE?

17:30.092 --> 17:31.963
YES, BUT I WAS
MAKING A JOKE

17:31.963 --> 17:34.444
ABOUT OTHER PEOPLE'S
PERCEPTIONS OF ME.

17:34.444 --> 17:35.924
SMART ENOUGH
NOT TO GET TRAPPED

17:35.924 --> 17:37.752
BY AN UNWANTED PREGNANCY,
