AND INTELLIGENCE

17:45.934 --> 17:48.067
AND MARTIAL-ARTS TALENT.

17:48.067 --> 17:50.721
OBJECTION --
MR. SILETTI IS ALWAYS

17:50.721 --> 17:53.550
