17:55.291 --> 17:58.251
SMART ENOUGH TO BUY YOUR WAY
OUT OF CRIMINAL CHARGES

17:58.251 --> 17:59.904
FROM HANNAH HARKINS,
RIGHT?

17:59.904 --> 18:02.603
