20:43.024 --> 20:45.548
THANKS, DAVE.

20:45.548 --> 20:48.725
I GOT YOUR BACK.

20:48.725 --> 20:51.728
TODAY, TOMORROW.

20:51.728 --> 20:54.296
WHENEVER.

20:54.296 --> 20:59.170
