23:54.955 --> 23:59.612
FOR A CRIME
WE CAN'T BE SURE...

23:59.612 --> 24:02.441
EVER HAPPENED.

24:02.441 --> 24:06.662
IF CINDY FELL DOWN HER STAIRS,

24:06.662 --> 24:10.492
