25:24.348 --> 25:26.699
HMM.

25:26.699 --> 25:30.746
SHE WAS LYING NAKED AND DEAD

25:30.746 --> 25:33.444
ON THE FLOOR
AT THE BOTTOM OF HER STAIRS,

25:33.444 --> 25:36.926
