BEHIND HER OWN LOCKED DOOR.

25:36.926 --> 25:40.103
NO SIGN OF ANY INTRUDER,

25:40.103 --> 25:42.453
NO EVIDENCE OF
ANY OTHER PRESENCE THAT NIGHT

25:42.453 --> 25:46.457
EXCEPT THE VICTIM
AND THE DEFENDANT.

25:46.457 --> 25:49.809
ALL THIS TALK ABOUT E-MAIL HACKS

25:49.809 --> 25:53.334
AND ANONYMOUS RELAYS
